        "translatedContent": ""
      },
      {
        "row": 2,
        "rowsha": "pP1lK7XykL/SEaWRBzHJoZ275fcHXUwtFjmF+IcIA2Q=",
        "originContent": "(Optional) Remove `~/ProtonDrive` if you no longer need the mount point.",
        "translatedContent": "(Optional) マウントポイントが不要になった場合は `~/ProtonDrive` を削除してください。"
      },
      {
        "row": 3,
        "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
        "originContent": "",
        "translatedContent": ""
      },
